Document: RenderSceneData
Path: godot/classes/class_renderscenedata.rst
Summary: Abstract scene data object for single viewport rendering, related to RenderSceneDataRD, RenderData, and RenderDataRD.

Abstract scene data object, exists for the duration of rendering a single viewport. See also RenderSceneDataRD, RenderData, and RenderDataRD.

Note: This is an internal rendering server object. Do not instantiate this class from a script.
